@startuml
title Corporate-to-bank supply chain finance (tsin)
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor #F0E9E1
  BorderColor #8A6D3B
}
skinparam ArrowColor #8A6D3B
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #F0E9E1
skinparam noteBorderColor #8A6D3B

[Supplier\n(seller)] as SUP
[Buyer] as BUY
[Bank / financier] as BANK

SUP --> BUY : delivers goods, issues invoice
SUP --> BANK : tsin.001 Invoice Financing Request
SUP --> BANK : tsin.006 Invoice Assignment Request
BANK --> SUP : tsin.002 / tsin.007 Status
SUP --> BANK : tsin.005 Undertaking Application
note bottom of BANK : an undertaking application feeds\nthe tsrv guarantee area
@enduml
